# DDD Strategic Hub & Workshop

High-level domain modeling and collaborative workshops.

## 🌪 Event Storming Workflow
1. Identify Domain Events
2. Identify Triggers (Commands)
3. Define Policies
4. Group into Aggregates
5. Define Bounded Contexts

## Strategic Patterns
- Ubiquitous Language
- Bounded Context Mapping (ACL, OHS)
- Subdomain Types (Core, Supporting, Generic)

## C4 Mapping
- Domain -> L1
- Bounded Context -> L2 (Container)
- Aggregates -> L3 (Component)
